/* BeginDocumentation
   Name: testsuite::test_GetConnections - sli script to test if GetConnections works as expected

   Synopsis: (test_getConnections) run

   Description:

   This test generates 100 iaf_neurons and connects them with different synapses.

   SeeAlso: GetConnections

   FirstVersion: May 2012
   Author: Marc-Oliver Gewaltig
 */

/unittest (7488) require
/unittest using

/iaf_neuron 100 Create /n Set

/sources [ 1 2 99 {} for ] def
/targets [ 2 2 100 {} for ] def

[sources targets] {Connect true} MapThread ;

% Retrieve all connections
<< >> GetConnections 0 get {cva} Map /conn Set

% extract the target entry from each connection id
conn { 1 get } Map /conn_targets Set

% this must match the original target list
targets conn_targets eq assert_or_die

% test if specific connections can be extracted
<< /source [1 3 99] >> GetConnections_D 0 get cva
{1 get } Map 
[2 4 100] eq assert_or_die

<< /target [2 4 100] >> GetConnections_D 0 get cva
{0 get } Map % extract source gids 
[1 3 99] eq assert_or_die



endusing
